175
00:18:58,640 --> 00:18:59,350
What do you think?

176
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:00,660
Beautiful place, isn't it?

177
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:06,590
Qiao Qingyu.

178
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:07,150
Hm?

179
00:19:08,740 --> 00:19:09,630
Close your eyes.

180
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:10,590
Why?

181
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:11,900
Just close them.

182
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:21,550
Don't open them until I tell you to.

183
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:23,590
What is it?

184
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,110
Be patient.

185
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:36,740
Open your eyes.

186
00:20:00,870 --> 00:20:02,030
How did you know?

187
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,350
I have my ways.

188
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:06,590
Make a wish.

189
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,260
What did you wish for?

190
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,740
For my first wish,

191
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:46,180
I hope I can get
into the university I want.

192
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:47,390
Second wish,

193
00:20:47,460 --> 00:20:49,400
I hope my whole family

194
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,310
stays healthy and safe.

195
00:20:51,870 --> 00:20:52,700
And the third?

196
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:54,740
I can't tell you.

197
00:20:54,830 --> 00:20:55,870
It's a secret.

198
00:20:58,310 --> 00:20:59,390
Thank you, Ming Sheng.

199
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:02,030
Don't mention it.

200
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,700
I'm going to get
into Jiangzhou University!

201
00:21:12,350 --> 00:21:13,310
Qiao Qingyu,

202
00:21:14,550 --> 00:21:15,980
I'm glad I met you.

203
00:21:18,390 --> 00:21:19,700
Me too!

204
00:21:22,260 --> 00:21:25,260
Let's both do well, all right?

205
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:27,460
All the best to us both.

206
00:21:27,937 --> 00:21:28,527
Yeah.

207
00:21:30,150 --> 00:21:31,630
(Every time I think about)

208
00:21:32,630 --> 00:21:33,920
(how growing up means)

209
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:35,550
