with my own efforts)

210
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:39,150
(and make my own choices,)

211
00:21:40,460 --> 00:21:42,500
(I can't wait to grow up faster.)

212
00:21:43,630 --> 00:21:44,310
(Qiao Qingyu.)

213
00:21:44,590 --> 00:21:45,030
(Hm?)

214
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:46,700
(The sun's up.)

215
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:48,980
It's time.

216
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,070
Ming Sheng,

217
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:13,070
do you think

218
00:22:14,220 --> 00:22:15,700
that once we grow up,

219
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:19,390
we'll meet so many people,

220
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:21,660
go through so many things,

221
00:22:22,420 --> 00:22:23,700
that all these memories

222
00:22:25,790 --> 00:22:27,550
we have now

223
00:22:29,260 --> 00:22:31,030
will mean nothing?

224
00:22:47,220 --> 00:22:47,870
Do you remember

225
00:22:47,870 --> 00:22:49,180
the first time we met?

226
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:52,900
You bit me.

227
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:56,310
I bit you back.

228
00:22:56,790 --> 00:22:58,220
Now we're even.

229
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:03,390
After this,
I'm going to delete all memories of you

230
00:23:05,390 --> 00:23:06,660
with a single click.

231
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,310
I wish you all the best.

232
00:23:14,420 --> 00:23:16,740
Hope you get
into the university you want.

233
00:24:24,940 --> 00:24:25,660
Qingyu!

234
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:27,940
The noodle shop's in trouble! Go!

235
00:24:27,940 --> 00:24:28,740
Hurry!

236
00:24:29,550 --> 00:24:30,790
Oh, the poor family.

237
00:24:31,220 --> 00:24:31,840
Look at them.

238
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:33,500
How do they expect
to do business like that?

239
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:53,030
Tastes worse than footbath water.

240
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:56,900
Listen to them. Filthy mouths.

241
00:24:57,260 --> 00:24:58,700
Watch your language!

242
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:01,150
Get out. Spit outside.

243
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:05,110
Didn't your teacher teach you?

244
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:06,420
Protect the environment.

245
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,180
Keep the place clean.

246
00:25:12,062 --> 00:25:13,102
Thanks for your hard work.

247
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:15,590
Mr. Qiao.

248
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:17,870
Don't mind them.

249
00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:19,790
Those boys don't know any better.

250
00:25:20,630 --> 00:25:22,180
You keep coming back here.

251
00:25:22,550 --> 00:25:24,310
We can't even do business anymore.

252
00:25:24,390 --> 00:25:25,830
What more do you want from us?

253
00:25:31,520 --> 00:25:32,550
Prospective mother-in-law.

254
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:34,900
Prospective father-in-law.

255
00:25:35,870 --> 00:25:37,420
