256
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:40,150
But I'm really not that petty.

257
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:42,350
I'm here today for a good reason.

258
00:25:42,830 --> 00:25:43,940
I swear.

259
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:45,030
Promise.

260
00:25:46,870 --> 00:25:47,830
I came here today

261
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:50,180
