266
00:25:56,740 --> 00:25:57,700
Just leave.

267
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:58,830
Qingyu.

268
00:25:58,830 --> 00:25:59,720
What do you mean?

269
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,980
Where do you think you're going?

270
00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:01,700
Stop!

271
00:26:02,630 --> 00:26:04,220
Please don't do this!

272
00:26:04,220 --> 00:26:05,220
What are you doing?

273
00:26:05,550 --> 00:26:07,110
Did I tell you to use force?

274
00:26:07,110 --> 00:26:07,870
Let go!

275
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:09,740
Did I tell you guys to do this?

276
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:14,830
Qingyu,

277
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,980
I'm just a man looking for love.

278
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:19,740
I'm not doing anything wrong.

279
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:20,870
Don't...

280
00:26:22,940 --> 00:26:23,830
Got a problem?

281
00:26:25,220 --> 00:26:25,940
No.

282
00:26:27,220 --> 00:26:28,030
Qingyu.

283
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:30,500
Age isn't a problem.

284
00:26:30,500 --> 00:26:31,390
If you choose me,

285
