294
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:48,220
Let him go, and I'll go with you!

295
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:49,220
Come on, then.

296
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:51,700
Move it!

297
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:53,600
Don't touch her!

298
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,790
Are you coming with me or not?

299
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:55,220
Fine.

300
00:26:55,220 --> 00:26:55,880
Let him go!

301
