317
00:28:19,870 --> 00:28:21,030
Go back to your room.

318
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:23,040
I'll stay here alone for a while.

319
00:28:23,040 --> 00:28:24,180
I'll head inside in a bit.

320
00:28:53,390 --> 00:28:54,260
Mom.

321
00:28:55,390 --> 00:28:58,110
Mom, what's wrong?

322
00:28:59,310 --> 00:29:01,150
