335
00:29:47,390 --> 00:29:49,700
You were as tiny as a kitten.

336
00:29:50,550 --> 00:29:52,420
You had tiny fingers.

337
00:29:54,180 --> 00:29:55,460
Tiny toes.

338
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:57,630
