It wasn't deformed at all.

344
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:16,740
Her cries were so loud and bright.

345
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:19,830
People thought she was a big baby.

346
00:30:26,350 --> 00:30:29,660
You're both my kids,

347
00:30:30,870 --> 00:30:32,900
