351
00:30:42,830 --> 00:30:44,030
You, though?

352
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:46,350
You were quiet since you were little,

353
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:49,830
never said much,

354
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:53,030
but you always had your own mind.

355
00:30:55,660 --> 00:30:57,900
Ever since we moved to Huanzhou,

356
00:31:00,310 --> 00:31:01,870
the family has gone through a lot.

357
00:31:03,150 --> 00:31:04,350
It's been even harder for you.

358
00:31:05,150 --> 00:31:07,390
New school environment,

359
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:10,030
