360
00:31:10,660 --> 00:31:13,030
So much pressure,
yet you kept improving.

361
00:31:18,870 --> 00:31:20,870
I see all of that.

362
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:25,260
You're a good kid.

363
00:31:26,220 --> 00:31:27,940
I just don't know why I always feel

364
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:32,110
the need to keep talking at you.

365
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:35,660
No, Mom. You don't talk too much.

366
00:31:36,390 --> 00:31:36,940
I...

367
00:31:39,420 --> 00:31:41,590
Every time I see how careful and timid

368
00:31:43,590 --> 00:31:45,260
you are around me,

369
00:31:45,870 --> 00:31:47,110
it breaks my heart.

370
00:31:48,310 --> 00:31:48,980
No...

371
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:50,030
But I just can't

372
00:31:50,460 --> 00:31:54,030
