373
00:31:54,390 --> 00:31:55,900
I'm scared.

374
00:31:55,940 --> 00:31:56,830
I'm scared...

375
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:00,630
Qingyu...

376
00:32:01,260 --> 00:32:03,180
I'm so scared...

377
00:32:04,110 --> 00:32:05,940
What are you going on about, Mom?

378
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:09,310
Your sister...

379
00:32:15,550 --> 00:32:16,740
Mom...

380
00:32:19,940 --> 00:32:22,550
I wasn't with her...

381
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:26,180
My poor girl went through so much...

382
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:28,660
In the end...

383
00:32:29,830 --> 00:32:30,740
She...

384
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:35,180
She's gone, but they still

385
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:38,030
point fingers at her. They still talked.

386
00:32:38,350 --> 00:32:40,420
She was just a child.

387
00:32:41,390 --> 00:32:44,830
What child doesn't make mistakes?

388
00:32:44,830 --> 00:32:48,390
If anyone was at fault,
it was me and her father...

389
00:32:52,070 --> 00:32:53,350
I regret it.

390
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:55,740
I regret

391
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:58,830
not letting her stay

392
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:02,260
when she came to Shunyun looking for us.

393
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:04,660
It was like I was possessed.

394
00:33:04,660 --> 00:33:06,420
She wanted to stay,

395
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:09,940
but somehow, I forced her to go back.

396
00:33:18,940 --> 00:33:21,310
I don't even know why...

397
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:22,870
I...

398
00:33:23,070 --> 00:33:24,980
I'm her mother...

399
00:33:25,700 --> 00:33:27,740
How could I do that?

400
00:33:27,830 --> 00:33:30,550
She was crying out for help to me...

401
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,900
Qingyu...

402
00:33:40,420 --> 00:33:44,310
I killed her...

403
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:48,390
Mom...

404
00:33:50,550 --> 00:33:53,790
I can't let it happen to you too.

405
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:57,870
I don't want you to live
the way your father and I did.

406
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,070
I...

407
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:03,870
Did I hurt you, Qingyu?

408
00:34:04,070 --> 00:34:05,560
I don't want to hurt you...

409
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:06,260
You're not, Mom...

410
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:07,460
I don't want to hurt you...

411
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:08,990
Mom, calm down...

412
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:10,910
I don't want to hurt you...

413
00:34:10,910 --> 00:34:13,550
I don't want you to turn out like us...

414
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:15,030
I just want you to have a good life.

415
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:17,070
I never meant to hurt you...

416
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:17,860
Mom...

417
00:34:17,990 --> 00:34:19,220
Did I hurt you, Qing?

418
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:20,220
No!

419
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:24,430
You said it yourself, Mom.

420
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:27,180
Yu and I are going to college.

421
00:34:27,180 --> 00:34:28,340
We'll find jobs,

422
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:30,300
