423
00:34:30,700 --> 00:34:32,220
We'll take care of you.

424
00:34:33,120 --> 00:34:34,590
You're going to live a good life too.

425
00:34:34,590 --> 00:34:36,340
Why are you rambling?

426
00:34:41,470 --> 00:34:42,150
Mom...

427
00:35:04,340 --> 00:35:05,110
Doctor,

428
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:07,780
I'm here to get another prescription
of sleeping pills for my mom.

429
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:14,180
How has she been lately?

430
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:16,070
Still having trouble sleeping?

431
00:35:16,910 --> 00:35:19,260
Most nights, she can only sleep a little
with the pills.

432
00:35:20,950 --> 00:35:23,070
We can adjust the dosage a little.

433
00:35:23,110 --> 00:35:24,550
But to be safe,

434
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,820
I still suggest
she come in for a visit herself.

435
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:28,300
I've told her many times.

436
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:29,740
She just won't come.

437
00:35:29,950 --> 00:35:31,380
Any other symptoms?

438
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:35,780
Her emotions are unstable.

439
00:35:36,470 --> 00:35:38,550
She zones out a lot

440
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:39,990
and cries when she's alone.

441
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,550
When you talk to her,

442
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:44,630
it's like she can't even hear you.

443
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:46,950
She used to be someone

444
00:35:46,950 --> 00:35:48,470
who was full of drive and energy.

445
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:52,300
Now it's like she's lost all motivation.

446
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:54,470
More than once,

447
00:35:54,950 --> 00:35:56,990
I've seen her just standing

448
00:35:56,990 --> 00:35:58,630
on the rooftop alone, in a daze.

449
00:35:58,660 --> 00:35:59,510
Have you noticed

450
00:35:59,510 --> 00:36:01,260
any signs of suicidal thoughts

451
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:03,070
or self-harm?

452
00:36:05,340 --> 00:36:06,550
Suicide?

453
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:21,300
(Based on what you've described,)

454
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:22,430
(your mother's depression)

455
00:36:22,430 --> 00:36:23,520
