456
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:26,180
(I strongly recommend she seek
medical treatment as soon as possible.)

457
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:28,400
(If necessary,
hospitalization might be needed.)

458
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,510
(Given her current state,)

459
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:32,150
(there's a very high risk of suicide.)

460
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:38,340
(As a family member,)

461
00:36:38,340 --> 00:36:39,550
(please stay alert.)

462
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:40,950
(Otherwise, with her condition,)

463
00:36:40,990 --> 00:36:43,470
(her life may be in danger
at any moment.)

464
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:20,110
Qingyu!

465
00:37:22,430 --> 00:37:23,220
Hurry up!

466
00:37:24,780 --> 00:37:25,590
Sit tight.

467
00:37:35,470 --> 00:37:36,380
Great!

468
00:37:37,430 --> 00:37:38,860
I need some water.

469
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:40,300
All right. Let's play four-on-four.

470
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,740
Same teams.

471
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:43,470
Tip-off.

472
00:37:43,470 --> 00:37:44,740
Tip-off! Game on!

473
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:48,550
Did you hear?

474
00:37:48,550 --> 00:37:50,150
It's Qiao Qingyu from Class 5.

475
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,630
Her family's in trouble again.

476
00:37:51,910 --> 00:37:53,150
The whole school knows by now.

477
00:37:53,380 --> 00:37:55,560
I heard the craziest part is her dad.

478
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:57,300
Yesterday,
he almost blew up the noodle shop

479
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:59,260
with a gas tank!

480
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,380
Qingyu.

481
00:38:14,700 --> 00:38:15,860
I'm being real with you today.

482
00:38:15,950 --> 00:38:16,780
I came alone.

483
00:38:17,110 --> 00:38:18,300
I'll buy you boba.

484
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:21,150
Or if you don't like that,

485
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:22,030
seafood, hot pot,

486
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,150
anything you want.

487
00:38:23,470 --> 00:38:24,820
Your sister used to love those.

488
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:26,740
You know why your sister

489
00:38:26,740 --> 00:38:28,260
was so famous back then?

490
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,660
It was all because of me.

491
00:38:30,070 --> 00:38:31,700
I posted

492
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:32,860
her best photos online.

493
00:38:32,860 --> 00:38:36,220
That's how she got
the title of "Shunyun's No. 1 Beauty."

494
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:38,470
I'm the real mastermind behind it all.

495
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:40,260
She was my creation.

496
00:38:41,740 --> 00:38:43,470
And how did she repay me?

497
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:45,380
She played with my feelings.

498
00:38:45,740 --> 00:38:47,910
But justice was served!

499
00:38:48,220 --> 00:38:50,070
Guess what I discovered at the hospital?

500
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:52,220
She had HIV.

501
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:00,510
The deeper I loved her,

502
00:39:01,630 --> 00:39:02,990
the more I hated her.

503
00:39:03,740 --> 00:39:04,950
So I leaked

504
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:06,380
the news online.

505
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:08,260
It blew up!

506
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:10,110
Everyone was talking about her.

507
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:13,590
"Shunyun's No. 1 Beauty has a disease."

508
00:39:14,740 --> 00:39:16,180
Her photos were everywhere.

509
00:39:16,860 --> 00:39:17,950
Comments flooded in.

510
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:19,510
They were all about your sister.

511
00:39:19,950 --> 00:39:21,590
It was better than a movie.

512
00:39:23,070 --> 00:39:24,470
Qiao Beiyu was sick.

513
00:39:25,260 --> 00:39:26,660
And you're the one who killed her.

514
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:28,780
You think I wanted to harass you?

515
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:31,150
You're the one who clung to me.
Don't you get that?

516
00:39:31,220 --> 00:39:32,590
Do you know how long it took me

517
00:39:32,590 --> 00:39:33,520
to forget all that pain?

518
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:34,760
She wouldn't have taken her life

519
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:36,040
if you hadn't posted it online!

520
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:37,430
What's it got to do with me?

521
00:39:37,910 --> 00:39:39,260
It's not my fault!

522
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:42,820
You posted it, didn't you?

523
00:39:43,660 --> 00:39:44,160
Didn't you?

524
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:46,040
If it weren't you,
would she have killed herself?

525
00:39:46,040 --> 00:39:47,080
You took advantage of her!

526
00:39:47,080 --> 00:39:47,910
How dare you!

527
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:49,220
You ruined our family!

528
00:39:49,220 --> 00:39:50,780
You're the murderer!

529
00:39:51,110 --> 00:39:52,220
Hei! Hei!

530
00:39:52,220 --> 00:39:53,030
It's all your fault!

531
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:53,590
Hei!

532
00:39:53,590 --> 00:39:54,550
Calm down, Hei.

533
00:39:54,550 --> 00:39:55,240
Enough!

534
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:55,910
What happened?

535
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:01,630
Are you okay?

536
00:40:03,150 --> 00:40:04,590
He killed Beiyu.

537
00:40:05,300 --> 00:40:06,150
What?

538
00:40:06,950 --> 00:40:08,070
He murdered her.

539
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:15,550
Something you should know, Hei.

540
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:17,550
She's dead.

541
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:19,430
They say she jumped into the sea.

542
00:40:20,430 --> 00:40:22,340
Who are you even talking about?

543
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:23,380
Qiao Beiyu.

544
00:40:23,380 --> 00:40:24,180
Who?

545
00:40:24,180 --> 00:40:25,110
Qiao Beiyu.

546
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:56,860
I didn't expect Hei to be the one

547
00:40:57,300 --> 00:40:59,180
who drove her sister to death.

548
00:41:00,150 --> 00:41:02,700
He killed her sister,
and still won't leave her alone.

549
00:41:03,680 --> 00:41:05,990
And the timing of it all.
The NCEE's just around the corner.

550
00:41:10,220 --> 00:41:11,220
Sheng.

551
00:41:11,220 --> 00:41:12,220
Don't overthink it.

552
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:13,880
There's nothing between you and her.

553
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:15,660
What happens to her has nothing to do
with you.

554
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:16,780
Yeah.

555
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:22,180
Sheng.

556
00:41:22,660 --> 00:41:24,740
You're going to Beining soon
for your exams.

557
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:25,550
Yeah.

558
00:41:25,550 --> 00:41:26,780
Got everything packed?

559
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,110
What time's your flight?

560
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:31,110
Bring me back

561
00:41:31,630 --> 00:41:33,110
two pairs of sneakers from Beining,

562
00:41:33,110 --> 00:41:33,820
