563
00:41:35,820 --> 00:41:36,950
Come on. Let's have a toast.

564
00:41:36,950 --> 00:41:38,600
To success and top marks on the exam.

565
00:41:38,600 --> 00:41:40,640
To good fortune,
and to never forgetting one another.

566
00:41:40,640 --> 00:41:40,910
Cheers.

567
00:42:40,861 --> 00:42:43,081
♪Maybe♪

568
00:42:44,941 --> 00:42:50,341
♪The more I care,
