00:43:09,541 --> 00:43:11,831
♪The future♪

572
00:43:13,531 --> 00:43:19,151
♪Time will unveil this mystery♪

573
00:43:20,731 --> 00:43:26,091
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

574
00:43:26,941 --> 00:43:33,251
♪But one that never expires♪

575
00:43:35,571 --> 00:43:40,621
♪Turns out, all my thoughts♪

576
00:43:40,721 --> 00:43:45,031
♪Spell your name♪

577
00:43:45,321 --> 00:43:51,331
♪The one and only stubbornness
in my heart♪

578
00:43:51,551 --> 00:43:54,861
♪From the very first glance♪

579
00:43:55,211 --> 00:43:59,281
♪I started painting
what our future would look like♪

580
00:43:59,281 --> 00:44:05,551
♪That's when the dream began
to feel real♪

581
00:44:05,551 --> 00:44:09,211
♪Turns out♪

582
00:44:09,531 --> 00:44:13,591
♪Your heart had a place for me too♪

583
00:44:13,991 --> 00:44:19,971
♪Cradling the same story we both knew♪

584
00:44:20,241 --> 00:44:23,901
♪Thankfully, we were naïve enough♪

585
00:44:23,901 --> 00:44:27,441
♪And brave just in time♪

586
00:44:27,441 --> 00:44:34,421
♪To make sure our moments
weren't lost to time♪

